<p><strong><a name="cantsubmit" id="cantsubmit"></a> I have completed my application for an LSC grant, but the system won’t let me submit it. How do I resolve this?</strong></p>
<p> The LSC Grants system will not allow a user to submit an incomplete application. Use the Review and Submit page to verify that all forms have been completed and all required uploads have been submitted. You will find a link to the Review and Submit page at the bottom of the blue navigation bar on the left-hand side of the page.</p>
