<p><i><a href="#top">Back to top</a></i></p>
<p><strong><a name="E1" id="E1"></a>Do I have to complete form E-1?</strong></p>
<p> Current LSC recipients <u><strong>do not</strong></u> complete form E-1 (Actual Staffing Information).</p>
<p><i><a href="#top">Back to top</a></i></p>
