<p>Below is an example of what a correctly formatted response would look like for <strong> Performance Area 4, Criteria 5, Inquiries 1 and 2</strong>.</p>
<p><strong>Performance Area 4, Criteria 5: Human resources administration</strong></p>
<ol>
